title: SO GD I am at the gay campus meet up thing.
body:
But I have my security textbook sections I need to read open on my phone and am just reading them.

Being serious its kinda obvious I don't fit in here. Too many cliques and I am literally sitting all alone at a table and people are literally standing lol.

I dunno. I am an ex med student who went comp sci. I don't fit in here. I don't care about the billion tumblr terms or tacky sexual jeers and comments. I just don't fit. Again. Even in the gay community that is "sooo" "accepting".

I dunno what I expected. I seriously am prolly gonna die alone. Not even joking. This shit is live.
